data.description:
Live in luxury on a corner lot in the Sanctuary. Marble entry with Cinderella staircase opens to Architectural Digest den with two-story windows, skybridge and gas fireplace with neo-classic mantle.
You'll love the gourmet kitchen which features cherry custom cabinets, slab granite counters, upgraded stainless appliances, sunny bfast nook, full wet bar and large keeping room. Gleaming owner's suite includes trey ceilings, spa bath with zero entry mosaic tile shower, sunken tub and diva closet. Call your friends! The backyard oasis with sun-shelf saltwater pool and hot tub + XL screened Florida patio and tile fire pit is an entertainer's dream.
Loads of extras: hardwood floors, elevator, Flambeaux gas lamps, separate office. walk-in closets, sprinkler system. In the heart of Mandeville, just blocks from the high school and the Causeway!
